What will be the output of the following code?

int[] arr = {1, 2, 3};
System.out.println(arr[2]);

What is the output of the following code?

for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
  System.out.print(i + " ");
}

What will be the output of the following code?

int[] arr = {4, 5, 6};
System.out.println(arr.length);

What is the result of this code snippet?

int sum = 0;
for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
  sum += i;
}
System.out.println(sum);
